{"tid":2488372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「如種族隔離」港府涉帶頭歧視","createTime":"2021-04-14T07:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T23:20:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4ada9e9647961b07efc7ce74c065152cb845304c","tid":2488372,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:48:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/TWRHWOTGXFHZZDIOTKUF7YSJVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FTWRHWOTGXFHZZDIOTKUF7YSJVM%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=f278a41e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FTWRHWOTGXFHZZDIOTKUF7YSJVM%2F&h=e4a48f88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/TWRHWOTGXFHZZDIOTKUF7YSJVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n「如種族隔離」港府涉帶頭歧視<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W7LH0gDTGBd1hp71KDduv3b60WI=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NZWJLHBUMRAJ3ENRXWWH3Z2B5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW7LH0gDTGBd1hp71KDduv3b60WI%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNZWJLHBUMRAJ3ENRXWWH3Z2B5Q.jpg&h=2b1e61de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李傲然<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府提出防疫措施，要求食肆員工及顧客接種疫苗後方可放寬社交距離，但現時30歲以下人士未獲安排接種。有未滿30歲的區議員批評政府「帶頭歧視」，造成社會分化。有電台聽眾更直斥安排猶如種族隔離政策，歧視不打針者。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭硬推安心碼：羨慕人哋清零<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30歲以下未可打針<br />\n<br />\n未滿30歲的油尖旺區議會議員李傲然批評政府帶頭歧視，造成社會分化，質疑政府希望社會盡快復原的說法，「我收到唔少未到30歲或非指定群組嘅居民反映，佢哋都想打疫苗，但未打得，佢哋嘅生命難道就不是生命嗎？」他認為政府有責任提供安全可靠和充足疫苗供市民揀選，「市民打唔打係一回事，但你唔可以唔提供呢個選擇，令不足30歲或唔係指定群組嘅人冇呢個選擇，會覺得被歧視，俾政府拋棄」。<br />\n<br />\n電台節目聽眾陳先生說，即使他已打針，也不會支持疫苗氣泡措施，尤其對clean zone安排感到憤怒，「令人諗到嗰啲種族隔離政策，白人就一邊，有色人種就另一邊，畀特權打咗針嘅人，同一時間又歧視嗰啲冇打針嘅人，我覺得係好離譜做法」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：食客分兩區 專家轟政府妄想<br />\n<br />\n政府下月推出「來港易」，免除來港的內地人14日檢疫及不需接種疫苗，反觀在港的市民若要進入酒吧及卡啦OK等場所，就須打針。<br />\n<br />\n電台節目聽眾吳先生批評對港人不公平，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷亦批評，「來港易」沒規定內地來港人士須打針，與疫苗氣泡甚至國策自相矛盾，「內地不停呼籲接種疫苗，你冇理由話唔使接種疫苗就可以嚟香港」。平機會昨日未能回答查詢。"},{"pid":"16aa42845613e1f791009c891aaad690ad03d7e5","tid":2488372,"uid":126590,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:54:41.000Z","msg":"食飯分開<br />\n<br />\n搭車又唔洗分？<br />\n<br />\n返工又唔洗分？<br />\n<br />\n行街又唔洗分？<br />\n<br />\n又同病毒傾掂數？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fATys03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfATys03.jpg&h=c3a59fbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e628f63ee933c8c6624f162335af73f193f0c94","tid":2488372,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"30歲以下嘅真係咁想打？未必喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d81c4995239023c45a398d65b77399154ad7149","tid":2488372,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16aa42845613e1f791009c891aaad690ad03d7e5","tid":2488372,"uid":126590,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:54:41.000Z","msg":"食飯分開<br />\n<br />\n搭車又唔洗分？<br />\n<br />\n返工又唔洗分？<br />\n<br />\n行街又唔洗分？<br />\n<br />\n又同病毒傾掂數？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fATys03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfATys03.jpg&h=c3a59fbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:43:29.000Z","msg":"武肺針本身就係病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2c9f43a9476804f45ca591cefc7a17788407fc","tid":2488372,"uid":364767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:50:28.000Z","msg":"成撚日蛇喱眼，態度鄙夷+語氣惡劣<br />\n777賤人個西樣 就係歧視界的代表人物"},{"pid":"4610740f1391fd3cdff761c2c3e121cc3825dc79","tid":2488372,"uid":18381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/excerpt